HEADWORD: Undefine
<hw>Un`de*fine"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>define</ets>.]</ety> <def>To make indefinite; to
obliterate or confuse the definition or limitations of.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

